data.name: Savory Breakfast Burrito
data.quickTastyDescription: A delicious breakfast burrito filled with scrambled eggs, cheese, and your choice of savory fillings, perfect for a quick, satisfying morning meal.
detailedCookingInstructions: Heat oil in a skillet over medium heat.
Add diced onion and bell pepper; saut√© until soft (about 3-4 minutes).
In a bowl, whisk the eggs with salt and pepper.
Pour the eggs into the skillet with the vegetables, scrambling until fully cooked.
Remove from heat and stir in cheese and cooked sausage or bacon.
Warm the tortillas in a separate pan or microwave.
Spoon the egg mixture into the center of each tortilla, fold, and roll into a burrito.
data.detailedName: Savory Breakfast Burrito with Eggs, Cheese, and Sausage
data.modifiersForBase: Add your choice of vegetables or proteins
